t: Field to sort by (prefix with - for descending) Webhooks:
Configure webhooks to receive real-time notifications when data changes. Supported events include: contact.created, contact.updated, deal.created, deal.stage_changed, deal.won, deal.lost, ticket.created, ticket.resolved. Webhook payloads are signed with HMAC-SHA256 for verification.

Error Handling:
All errors return a consistent JSON structure:
{
  "error": {
    "code": "RESOURCE_NOT_FOUND",
    "message": "Contact with ID 12345 was not found",
    "status": 404
  }
}

